<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>How is the twitch of a muscle fiber related to the silent explosion of a supernova? Every happening is linked at an atomic level by the principles of chemistry. Chemists analyze substances, test environmental samples, create new substances, and test theories using chemical analysis. They also measure the properties of substances, like the strength of materials used in engineering.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
